<h1>Rust IDE and Editor Setup Guide</h1>

<p>The Rust Language Server (RLS) provides a standard interface for IDEs,
editors and tools to interact with Rust. For users, it's a hassle free
solution to get Rust working with your favourite IDE or editor.</p>

<p>The RLS team develops an extension for
<a href="http://code.visualstudio.com/">Visual Studio Code</a>, so if you
do not have a preferred editor, we recommend it for a smooth user
experience.</p>

